In the INTEREST OF C.T., R.T., and C.T., Minor Children, R.T., Father, Appellant. No. 18-1958 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A father appeals a juvenile court order terminating his parental rights to three children. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
